Working document - Nothing is final

AdaFruit IO Feed API: 

The application will accept the following string formats.  The first parameter is a description of what is being sent, 
the content is delimited with a ';'

colors are RGBA format. 
    A valid color would be:  255,255,255,255
    this is solid color white

seconds_to_disappear is a whole number/int.  After that many seconds have passed, the notification will
hide and the screen will return home.  If this is left blank, the screen will have to manually be exited

info;color;dataMainText[,dataSubText];title;imageUrl;seconds_to_disappear

image;url;color;seconds_to_disappear


